peddlers is a 2012 indian hindi crime thriller film written and directed by vasan bala . the film features gulshan devaiah , nishikant kamat , kriti malhotra ( of dhobi ghat fame ) , nimrat kaur and siddharth menon in the lead roles . the film was screened as part of 2012 international critics ' week , an independent film event which runs parallel to the cannes film festival in southern france . film 's producer , guneet monga raised nearly ₹ 1 crore ( us$ 160,000 ) , half of film 's budget of ₹ 2 crore ( us$ 310,000 ) by posting the film 's script on facebook .